{"tid":2145100,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"藍店車仔面黎講 文記好食定任你點好食?","createTime":"2020-08-08T01:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T11:45:43.000Z","uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9daf5c569ad2ef40b7885419f17a0d61fde8d919","tid":2145100,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"文記 味精湯底+5倍糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬紅 大腸有質素 次次去蔗汁糖水必飲<br />\n係加價加到癲 以前6蚊餸變到11蚊<br />\n夜晚成日有阿sir買上車食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任老點 下午茶幾平 $30蚊包野飲<br />\n上次同個女仔fd去食 <br />\n佢叫茶餐B 蛋、叉燒、菜<br />\n我叫茶餐D 5餸盲包<br />\n點知黎到我果份有 蛋 叉燒 菜 仲有紫菜 墨丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢覺得被人昆即刻眼濕濕話唔食 走左<br />\n<br />\n我本身諗住aa制 唔夠錢比<br />\n好彩枱面寫住收支付寶 仲支持花唄<br />\n先借到錢比 唔洗比班mk打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9567c7c6c1a844fd23faf29a1f21f10a4be12ab3","tid":2145100,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"花唄係個app定咩<br />\n借錢架？"},{"pid":"82b7be2d7705f4c62f2332ec58ed8298cf89ec85","tid":2145100,"uid":283700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9567c7c6c1a844fd23faf29a1f21f10a4be12ab3","tid":2145100,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"花唄係個app定咩<br />\n借錢架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"可能係花同貝殼。都幾原始喎"},{"pid":"d3578434c3c9bd52e1720815cae8c5c9b3e04bc8","tid":2145100,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9567c7c6c1a844fd23faf29a1f21f10a4be12ab3","tid":2145100,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"花唄係個app定咩<br />\n借錢架？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"支付寶版信用卡"},{"pid":"1c404a55257098cd4c6c28363658803a3a572433","tid":2145100,"uid":4174,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"任你點一早黃 打手玩屈？"},{"pi